# Keep the Docker build context clean + reproducible (matches a fresh git
# checkout, which is what Coolify builds from). Without this, a local
# `docker build` copies host node_modules/.next into the image and can mask
# missing-dependency bugs that only surface on Coolify's clean checkout.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/.git
.git
.claude
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
packages/dev/src-tauri/target
